                    <msContents class="lemmatic">
                        <summary>
                            The manuscript contains the following works:
                            1) Abd Latif Baghdadi's commentary on the Aphorisms in <locus>ff. 1a-132b</locus>;
                            2) a short extract from his commentary on Epidemics in <locus>ff. 132b-133a</locus>;
                            3) his commentary on Prognostics in <locus>ff. 134a-186b</locus>.
                            4) the rest of the folio is On Anatomy in <locus>ff. 187a-230b</locus>. 
                            Item 1 is a lemmatically arranged commentary. It lacks the introduction.The beginning of each Book is as follows:
                        </summary>
